  "description": "Implement CMS Program Management for Multi-language Content\n\nEnsure the Content Management System can properly manage and display programs for English (en) and Polish (pl) languages in the admin interface.\n\nRequirements:\n- Investigate why programs are not visible in the admin page for en and pl languages\n- Verify program data exists in the database for both language variants\n- Ensure proper database queries retrieve programs by language code\n- Fix any UI rendering issues preventing program display in admin interface\n- Test that program management (create, edit, delete) works for both languages\n- Verify language switching functionality works correctly in admin panel\n- Ensure proper error handling when programs are missing for a language",
